sql_query.sql: SELECT "user_ips".* FROM "user_ips" WHERE "user_ips"."user_id" = $1 ORDER BY "user_ips"."user_id" ASC LIMIT $2

SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."updated_at" FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "statuses"."account_id" INNER JOIN "statuses_tags" ON "statuses_tags"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."visibility" = $1 AND "accounts"."suspended_at" IS NULL AND "accounts"."silenced_at" IS NULL AND "statuses_tags"."tag_id" = $2 AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM statuses_tags forbidden WHERE forbidden.status_id = statuses.id AND forbidden.tag_id IN (NULL))) GROUP BY "statuses"."id" ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $3
